00:42:26,573 --> 00:42:27,293
I wonder when we can

910
00:42:27,453 --> 00:42:28,413
find any clue.

911
00:42:33,693 --> 00:42:34,373
Xiaoran.

912
00:42:36,373 --> 00:42:37,533
Thank you for helping me

913
00:42:38,133 --> 00:42:38,893
and keeping me company.

914
00:42:39,133 --> 00:42:40,013
I'm not.

