00:42:42,853 --> 00:42:44,613
I've been meaning to tell you

916
00:42:45,093 --> 00:42:46,373
I did all these

917
00:42:46,653 --> 00:42:47,373
because

918
00:42:47,573 --> 00:42:48,333
I want the wicked Zhao Mingxuan

919
00:42:48,453 --> 00:42:49,573
to be arrested,

920
00:42:49,693 --> 00:42:50,493
and that's all.

921
00:42:59,453 --> 00:43:00,733
What do you plan to do next?

922
00:43:02,253 --> 00:43:03,013
Let me send you home first.

