00:43:18,522 --> 00:43:21,482
♪Memory suddenly stops♪

924
00:43:23,282 --> 00:43:27,002
♪Did I miss you too much?♪

925
00:43:29,562 --> 00:43:32,002
♪The junction in the past♪

